Regression test for input validation of SET PARTITION NUMDBS / NUMCOLS / DBS / COLS / SHARDS.
- oversized NUMDBS or NUMCOLS values must be rejected with an error (not crash the server)
- the original crash path: NUMDBS=2147483647 caused malloc(~16 GB) to return NULL, and the
  subsequent SET PARTITION DBS write to that NULL pointer caused a server crash
- server must remain reachable after receiving all invalid inputs
